subproject.corporate outcome: National, regional and local levels of governance expand their capacities to manage the equitable delivery of public services
subproject.description:
Following are key outputs of the project:
1. Establishment of the Target Centre (TC) in Head Department of Air Transport 
2. Increasing capacities of customs personnel in application of the new technologies and operation management
3. Familiarization with best practices in target definition field.
